Reduce claims data to possible large claims

reduce_data.Rd

The original dataframe is reduced to possible large claims to save computing time in the next steps.

This is not yet a precise separation as the indexed columns are missing at this point.

This function resembles only step 1 of the data preparation process, see description in details of prepare_data()

Usage

reduce_data(claims_data, indices, threshold)

Arguments

claims_data

dataframe, see details of prepare_data().

indices

dataframe, see details of prepare_data().

threshold

numeric value to separate small from large claims, see details of prepare_data().

Value

subset of dataframe claims_data where preselected small claims have been eliminated
